        android:text='1 cup 8oz/240g unsalted butter, melted and cooled 2 tablespoons (30ml) vegetable oil 1 1/4 cups (9oz/260g) white sugar 1 cup (7oz/200g) packed light brown sugar 4 (2oz/57g each) large eggs, at room temperature 1 tablespoon (15ml) pure vanilla extract 3/4 teaspoon salt 1 cup (3.5oz/130g) all purpose flour 1 cup (3.5oz/100g) good quality, unsweetened cocoa powder 7 oz (200g) roughly chopped chocolate or large chocolate chips"'
        app:layout_constraintTop_toBottomOf="@+id/textView"
